title: La flor
language: Catalan, Spanish, French, English, Russian, German, Swedish
actors: Elisa Carricajo, Valeria Correa, Pilar Gamboa, Laura Paredes, Esteban Lamothe, Pablo Seijo, Luciana Acuña, Paula Acuña, Coyi Aguiar, Azul Aizenberg, Juanse Segundo Alamos, Fernanda Alarcón, Pablo Coya Albornoz, Eugenia Alonso, María Rosa Andreotti
description: A film in six episodes, connected by the same four actresses, full of various subplots that play with narrative and different cinematic genres , everything structured in an unusual way.
